{"tid":1837132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制TVB日任(23/2)：陳煒 X 樂斯牌家電","createTime":"2020-01-23T13:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:11:06.000Z","uid":75759,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"55b89fbb005d464bce00c57a6e331920e67b4282","tid":1837132,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留言無必要有威嚇成份<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住表達客戶意見係我地個權利</span><br />\n不被捕係大原則</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">記得bookmark: <br />\nTVB廣告商永久抵制名單！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD[/size=]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD%5B%2Fsize%3D%5D&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=eeff2685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD[/size=]</a></div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">未來方向：</span><br />\n聯絡各大黃色經濟APP，擺TVB廣告商上去，方便大家</div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【永久抵制精選@23 Jan 2020】<br />\n💎樂斯牌 X 陳煒💎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QrgWRvE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrgWRvE.jpg&h=67783a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n👇🏻😡去樂斯牌專頁派嬲兼留言！👇🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NutzenGermany/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNutzenGermany%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a80dec16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NutzenGermany/</a><br />\n👇🏻😢去陳煒Facebook 勸佢離開TVB！👇🏻 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chanwai1121/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchanwai1121%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=fbfef4b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chanwai1121/</a><br />\n<br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2.請願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️樂斯牌好危險❗️<br />\n電磁爐<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不符安全要求</span></strong>🍳<br />\n循環扇分分鐘<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">夾手指</span></strong>☝️😱<br />\n想安全過新年，勿買陳煒代言樂斯牌🚫<br />\n<br />\n消委會推介：SPT / Olympia / Gemini / 德國卓爾Summe / 奧高Origo<br />\n<br />\n[Source]<br />\n電磁爐 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/37l3gxl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37l3gxl&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=6398a8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/37l3gxl</a><br />\n循環扇 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RIZyqU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RIZyqU&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=f33697a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2RIZyqU</a><br />\n<br />\n#陳煒 #樂斯牌<br />\n<br />\n※留言template<br />\n<blockquote>抵制TVB運動已開始半年，貴公司仍然用無綫電視藝人作代言實屬不智，本人深表遺憾，並呼籲貴公司停止與無綫藝人合作，否則將永久抵制貴公司，敬請注意。<br />\n<br />\n唔止用TVB龔慈恩代言，仲成日請TVB偽人做分享😡<br />\nTVB咁鍾意報假新聞，旗下偽人代言又點會靠得住❓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幾幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gz9EPhO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz9EPhO.jpg&h=71ec3fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoFMuhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoFMuhP.jpg&h=bfeac61d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqGsdKw.png\" data-